+## Overview
+
+Total revenue across the period was $7,154.44 from 30 orders. The median order value is $204.94, while the average order is roughly $238.48. Sales span four regions and four products, with Gadget generating the most revenue despite modest unit counts thanks to its $149.50 price.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget leads at $2,392.00, driven by price rather than volume. Widget follows at $2,118.94 on steady demand across every region. Doohickey contributes $1,513.00, and Sprocket trails at $1,130.50 despite large unit quantities, reflecting its low $4.75 price point.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North is the strongest region at $2,176.35, followed by East at $1,830.79 and South at $1,732.48. West trails at $1,414.82. The gap between the top and bottom regions is about $761, indicating fairly balanced but uneven coverage.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget stock and promotion; it drives the most revenue per order at the highest price point.
+- Support the West region, lowest at $1,414.82, with targeted campaigns to close the regional gap.
+- Reassess Sprocket pricing or bundling; high volume yields only $1,130.50, the weakest product return.
